Hedge Funds, Private Equity Pose System Risk, Handelsblatt Says

-- B y   B r i a n   P a r k i n
-- 
2011-09-06T06:16:34Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-06/hedge-funds-private-equity-pose-system-risk-handelsblatt-says.html
Hedge funds and private equity
investors pose a significant risk to the stability of the
financial system, Gustav Horn, the director of  Germany ’s IMK
economic institute told  Handelsblatt  newspaper in an interview.  The practice of short selling can destabilize the financial
system as the investors’ links to banks grow, Horn is cited as
saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Brian Parkin in Berlin at 
 bparkin@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James Hertling at 
 jhertling@bloomberg.net  